{"tid":1951485,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"何栢良倡武漢肺炎穩定患者往另一處隔離　由警員把守","createTime":"2020-03-31T04:20:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-31T04:46:15.000Z","uid":184679,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9febc5c0ed5f1d295a54a77b9a870b4c51a87e35","tid":1951485,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T04:20:52.000Z","msg":"港大感染及傳染病中心總監何栢良表示，香港要盡快建立類似內地「方艙醫院」的地方，安排病情穩定又未能出院的新型肺炎患者到有關地點，接受嚴厲的隔離，直至所有檢測都呈陰性。他說，不能安排這類病人回家，認為這是危險的做法。<br />\n<br />\n何栢良在一個網台節目表示，有關地點一定要有警員把守，以免病人有機會逃走而進入社區，該處的通風系統亦要加強，而且要採取加強感染控制措施，例如要求病人戴口罩等。<br />\n<br />\n何栢良說，現時未有這樣的安排，導致醫院沒有空間收新症，但亦不能勉強安排病人入院，否則會增加其他病人及醫護受感染機會。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1517917-20200331.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1517917-20200331.htm&d=C7qEe2dSMr%2BabA5wG5krtMlSugA1I0CCabXjLbCjl00%3D&h=42e546d6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1517917-20200331.htm&h=6dc05393\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1517917-20200331.htm</a>"},{"pid":"2c5bdbfcedfab09e2a2323e9ef4473d107964f73","tid":1951485,"uid":90521,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T04:22:11.000Z","msg":"咁班狗一定話唔夠人，之後就係社區隔離算<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3db43f2acaf8b0aaf03dd4551b511dfb4a03ef7a","tid":1951485,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T04:23:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7bf31c3539b7c7b965ac6f1beeccf29ec916935","tid":1951485,"uid":14494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T04:25:02.000Z","msg":"最後又係民安隊pt價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d02035daefd8f785622216fea354866e3cc082a5","tid